{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When the rain no longer travels with the wind, but rushes indoors, it turns into \u201cthe escaping rain\u201d .</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Why does this strange weather happen?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mushroom, an investigator of curious cases, receives a vague request to investigate a house, but the owner of the house, the carpenter Cielo, seems to have the slightest inkling of it. A weird atmosphere pervades the place, with strange wooden ears everywhere, \u201cThey seem to have popped up recently, probably because it's been raining for too long.\u201d</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll play as Mushroom, tracking down clues and solving mysteries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Mushroom Investigates into Curious Cases: the Escaping Rain</i> is a point-and-click adventure puzzle game developed by slowicrowi.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game length: 0.5-2 hours</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>How to play:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Left mouse button: Move/Interact/Confirm</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Right mouse button: Call out menu/Cancel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3547650/extras/mogucolor.gif?t=1740245446\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Game Features:</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Imaginative art style</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Fall down the rabbit hole and embark on a fantasy adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3547650/extras/AF549656B5109C25C1FE979ED4F4BDBF.png?t=1740245446\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Immersive clue-collecting experience</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-You can in